        <h2 class="title"><a href="/node/251">Theology Rocks Show #60 - &quot;Getting Doctrines Right... and How We Get Them Wrong&quot;</a> <span id="nodetoggle-251" style="cursor: pointer; " title="show details for Theology Rocks Show #60 - &quot;Getting Doctrines Right... and How We Get Them Wrong&quot;"></span></h2>        <div id="collapsinode-251">
        <div class="content"><p>Primarily it&#39;s a discussion about the importance of the doctrine of the resurection, but we discuss a whole range of things, and how we, as humans, tend to screw them up. If there&#39;s a particular doctrine you&#39;d like to discuss with us, let us know. </p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
