        <h2 class="title"><a href="/node/249">Theology Rocks Show #59 - &quot;Desperately Searching for Lost Sheep&quot;</a> <span id="nodetoggle-249" style="cursor: pointer; " title="show details for Theology Rocks Show #59 - &quot;Desperately Searching for Lost Sheep&quot;"></span></h2>        <div id="collapsinode-249">
        <div class="content"><p>Perhaps we don&#39;t get excited enough about &quot;missing sheep.&quot; When someone in our congregation drops off the radar, we should go after them, with fear for their lives</p>
<hr/>
